business' together with the installation of a new press had caused
disruption and pressure on margins.
Group turnover improved to Pounds 24.5m (Pounds 20.1m).
The interim dividend is lifted from 1.1p to 1.2p, payable from earnings per
share of 2.92p (2.3p).
